</picture></div></div><div
class="block-intro-text"><p>A nail salon is a fun, social, and creative way to make money. As a relatively easy market to break into, owning a nail salon can be a rewarding experience that offers you the opportunity to make up to $75,000 a year. If you have a passion for the beauty industry and are interested in starting your own business, read through our detailed guide.</p></div></div></div></div><div
