@type":"HowToStep","position":"2","name":"<p>Ensure that cleanliness standards are followed.<\/p>\n","text":"<p>Careful steps should be taken to keep nail salon instruments clean, as it is easy for bacteria, fungi, and even viruses to be transferred between customers and employees.<\/p>\n<p>The U.S. Environmental Protection Agency has published a guide for nail salon owners titled \"<a href=\"https:\/\/nepis.epa.gov\/Exe\/ZyPDF.cgi\/60000F3A.PDF?Dockey=60000F3A.PDF\">Protecting the Health of Nail Salon Workers<\/a>,\" which provides best practices related to sanitizing instruments and ensuring safety and cleanliness in the salon.<\/p>\n","url":"https://www.zarla.com/guides/how-to-start-a-nail-salon#how-to-start-a-nail-salon-section8-step2","image":{"@type":"ImageObject","url":"https://www.zarla.com/images/zarla-ensure-that-cleanliness-standards-are-followed-288x288-20200817.jpeg?crop=1:1,smart&width=144&dpr=2","height":"288","width":"288"},"itemListElement":[{"@type":"HowToTip","text":"<p>State and local requirements may differ, so be sure to contact your local cosmetology board or state health department for more information.<\/p>\n"}]}]},{"@type":"HowToSection","position":"9","name":"<p>Market your nail salon.<\/p>\n","itemListElement":[{"@type":"HowToStep","position":"1","name":"<p>Create social media profiles.<\/p>\n","text":"<p>Social media is a great way to build brand awareness, engage with current customers, and attract new ones. Since your services are visual, open an Instagram and Facebook account to post images of your manicures and pedicures.<\/p>\n<p>Bear in mind that customers are always on the look-out for proof that your nail salon meets their expectations of quality service.<\/p>\n","url":"https://www.zarla.com/guides/how-to-start-a-nail-salon#how-to-start-a-nail-salon-section9-step1","image":{"@type":"ImageObject","url":"https://www.zarla.com/images/zarla-create-social-media-accounts-288x288-20200812.jpeg?crop=1:1,smart&width=144&dpr=2","height":"288","width":"288"}},{"@type":"HowToStep","position":"2","name":"<p>Ensure that your nail salon can be found in an internet search.<\/p>\n","text":"<p>Does your nail salon pop up on Google when you search \"where can I find the best nail salon near me?\" You can boost your chances of appearing in local search results by creating a profile on various business platforms and signing up for Google My Business and Yelp! There's also pay-per-click (PPC) advertising for boosting traffic to your website.<\/p>\n","url":"https://www.zarla.com/guides/how-to-start-a-nail-salon#how-to-start-a-nail-salon-section9-step2","image":{"@type":"ImageObject","url":"https://www.zarla.com/images/zarla-sign-up-for-google-my-business-288x288-20200812_2023-09-26-044019_bjsm.jpeg?crop=1:1,smart&width=144&dpr=2","height":"288","width":"288"}},{"@type":"HowToStep","position":"3","name":"<p>Take an online course to boost your knowledge and skills.<\/p>\n","text":"<p>If you're not skilled in social media management, consider taking an online search engine marketing (SEM) and\/or search engine optimization (SEO) course or contact a local agency to help you reach your marketing goals.<\/p>\n","url":"https://www.zarla.com/guides/how-to-start-a-nail-salon#how-to-start-a-nail-salon-section9-step3","image":{"@type":"ImageObject","url":"https://www.zarla.com/images/zarla-take-an-online-course-288x288-20200812.jpeg?crop=1:1,smart&width=144&dpr=2","height":"288","width":"288"}},{"@type":"HowToStep","position":"4","name":"<p>Offer customers a discount or birthday special.<\/p>\n","text":"<p>This is a great way to let people know about the new nail salon in the area and what they can look forward to. Perhaps you'd like to offer customers 10% off their first manicure or a discount on their birthday.<\/p>\n","url":"https://www.zarla.com/guides/how-to-start-a-nail-salon#how-to-start-a-nail-salon-section9-step4","image":{"@type":"ImageObject","url":"https://www.zarla.com/images/zarla-offer-customers-a-discount-or-birthday-special-288x288-2020101.jpeg?crop=1:1,smart&width=144&dpr=2","height":"288","width":"288"}}]},{"@type":"HowToSection","position":"10","name":"<p>Increase your revenue.<\/p>\n","itemListElement":[{"@type":"HowToStep","position":"1","name":"<p>Upsell to customers.<\/p>\n","text":"<p>Depending on your target market, selling premium nail care products that are not available in drug stores and shops is a great way to earn extra income. Think high-end nail polish brands like Morgan Tailor and OPI. <\/p>\n<p>Bear in mind that holding this stock will also create a cash flow need, which must be factored into your financial projections.<\/p>\n<p>Consider stocking moisturizers, cuticle oil, nail clippers, and other products related to hand and feet maintenance. This will entice your clients to buy additional products to take home with them, and also attract people walking by your salon.<\/p>\n","url":"https://www.zarla.com/guides/how-to-start-a-nail-salon#how-to-start-a-nail-salon-section10-step1","image":{"@type":"ImageObject","url":"https://www.zarla.com/images/zarla-sell-retail-products-to-customers-288x288-20200817.jpeg?crop=1:1,smart&width=144&dpr=2","height":"288","width":"288"}},{"@type":"HowToStep","position":"2","name":"<p>Draw attention with a beautiful display.<\/p>\n","text":"<p>Decide on the most appropriate way to display and stock your high-end products to create awareness and allow customers to browse and buy these products easily.<\/p>\n","url":"https://www.zarla.com/guides/how-to-start-a-nail-salon#how-to-start-a-nail-salon-section10-step2","image":{"@type":"ImageObject","url":"https://www.zarla.com/images/zarla-draw-attention-with-a-beautiful-display-288x288-20200817.jpeg?crop=1:1,smart&width=144&dpr=2","height":"288","width":"288"}}]}]}</script> <div
